data.description: Assumable VA loan with a 2.25% mortgage rate. Must be assumed by another VA. Significant cost savings for qualified buyers.Great solar contract with no True Up. Monthly payment averages around $160 a month.Turnkey and spacious smart home located in Stallion Springs 3BR/2BA solar powered home with over 2400 square feet of living space and an 800 square foot detached 3 car garage. Beautiful flat corner lot with drought tolerant landscaping and RV parking. This home is on Natural Gas and Public Sewer. This perfectly priced home is centrally located in a prime location. Walking distance to the pool, community center, restaurants and parks. The school bus stop is conveniently located across the street.This stunning single story home welcomes you from the moment you walk through the front door. Once you enter the heart of the home, it opens to a great room, dining room and spacious kitchen. This split-wing home features two spacious bedrooms and a bathroom on one side of the home. On the other side of the home, it features a large laundry room with ample storage that leads you into a massive 400 square foot family room that can be used as a hobby room, office space, library, children's play area, exercise room, billiard room, craft room or theater room. This great room has endless possibilities. Retreat to your beautiful primary suite, designed for ultimate relaxation with a large walk-in closet. The private spa-like bathroom includes a large soaking tub, separate shower and dual vanities.This move-in ready home also features an alarm system, motion sensor lights, solar landscaping lights, smart stove, smart washer/dryer, fridge, concealed fire sprinkler heads in the ceilings, tankless water heater, 2 ft of insulation in the attic, double pane windows, rain gutters, large tuff shed and whole house generator plug.
